- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as text readability assessment can be seen as a subtask of information retrieval. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also encompass the topic of the paper. 
- cs.EDU (Education) is less likely but still possible as the paper focuses on texts tailored for L2 learners.
